  "title": "Legal Senior Specialist",
  "description": "<p><strong>Legal & Compliance Senior Specialist</strong></p><p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p><ul><li>Monitor\n     and interpret data protection laws relevant to the business</li><li>Develop,\n     implement and maintain data protection policies, frameworks, SOP for data\n     breach incidents (data breach response and reporting procedures for\n     regional incidents)</li><li>Conduct\n     regular privacy risk assessments and data mapping</li><li>Assist\n     in drafting, updating and implementing compliance policies, procedures and\n     controls</li><li>Support\n     the delivery of compliance programs to employees</li><li>Support\n     with drafting and reviewing of legal documents, contracts and policies</li><li>Assist\n     in legal and regulatory issues as required</li><li>Support\n     budgeting and invoice processing and other administrative support</li></ul><p><strong>Qualifications: </strong></p><ul><li>Degree\n     in Legal and/or compliance background</li><li>Strong\n     understanding of personal data protection laws, regulations, principles\n     and best practices in the region</li><li>3-5\n     years’ working experience</li><li>Meticulous,\n     team player, proficient in Office Apps</li></ul><p>Please feel free to reach out to Carol <a href=\"mailto:carol.sun@peopleprofilers.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">carol.sun@peopleprofilers.com<br /></a>Reg. Number: R25129558 | EA License Number: 02C4944<a href=\"mailto:carol.sun@peopleprofilers.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><br /></a></p>",
